comments.body:
While working on a manifest list feature , I stumbled upon this issue and I found it difficult to find what is happening at first, I think by default we should allow pushing all images in manifest list and allow pushing manifest without images if there is any special need i.e `--omit-images` or something similar.

Reason is that I don't think by default any body would like to push flat manifest list without images, cause I don't see lot of use-cases there. So I think we should flip this logic ( but this is just my opinion :) and not a strong one )

@containers/buildah-maintainers @containers/podman-maintainers WDYT ?
